
### ==================== HOTEL CRUD ====================

### GET all hotels
GET http://localhost:3000/api/hotels

###
### GET hotel by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/2

###
### CREATE new hotel
POST http://localhost:3000/api/hotels
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Grandeur Palace Hotel",
    "location": "Bangkok",
    "rating": 5,
    "contact": "+66-2-123-4567"
}

###
### CREATE another hotel
POST http://localhost:3000/api/hotels
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Riverside Resort",
    "location": "Chiang Mai",
    "rating": 4,
    "contact": "+66-5-987-6543"
}

###
### UPDATE hotel by ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Grandeur Palace Hotel - Updated",
    "rating": 4.5
}

###
### DELETE hotel by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/2